{"tid":1601684,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"雖然她是加拿大籍港人，但強調自己是一名愛國人士","createTime":"2019-09-29T06:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T06:55:57.000Z","uid":293018,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"77232a595f7d7560b1b55ed7cf3fa0a5870c4b0e","tid":1601684,"uid":293018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T06:34:53.000Z","msg":"港政研會舉辦愛國愛港活動　受訪者：尊重我們的國家<br />\n一場由香港政研會主辦的愛國愛港活動，今早首先在尖沙咀文化中心廣場外舉行，隨後又挪到香港太平山頂外的廣場，目的是慶祝中華人民共和國國慶70週年。<br />\n<br />\n一名活動參與者向《聯合早報》記者說，雖然她是加拿大籍港人，但強調自己是一名愛國人士。&ldquo;我們是中國人，basically（基本上）我們不會說自己是香港人。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n這位女士說，她是從愛國愛港的港人朋友那邊得知有這些活動，她們的活動方式目主要是唱國歌、&ldquo;respect（尊重）我們的國家&rdquo;，以及祝賀中國國慶70週年。<br />\n<br />\n被問到是否擔心反修例人士會影響她們的愛國活動，她回應說：&ldquo;不會，不可以害怕這麼多，他們（反修例人士）就最大嗎？我們是silent majority （沉默的大多數），現在要出來了...不要以為黑衣人會打、會罵人，就威，我們只是出來唱國歌，支持我們的國家，我們不會打人、不會戴面罩，We love China（我們愛中國）！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.zaobao.com/realtime/china/story20190929-992977\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.zaobao.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2Fstory20190929-992977&d=kT0D7NwRktyFNYuHQ%2Fv%2Be6Zg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=4dc02056\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.zaobao.com/realtime/china/story20190929-992977</a><br />\n嚴重懷疑佢入籍加拿大發假誓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e206eff1b35ab3ecb8bd7bbecb8a975742fb66","tid":1601684,"uid":105340,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T06:44:44.000Z","msg":"有樣就得<br />\n黎支持搞到 冇左加籍"},{"pid":"a47c2b20908686029bec57feec1c0c4e9eb61b03","tid":1601684,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T06:46:39.000Z","msg":"冷氣軍師做吓野"},{"pid":"daa5b0eb347b9de2c01d1647ed525e27798312a0","tid":1601684,"uid":281539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T06:47:56.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"f98165fefc80c652bae424660f09f49ba1ac1b6a","tid":1601684,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T06:55:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"}]}